Title: KitchenAid® Dough Blade
Description: Provides kneading action when making yeast dough. Works only with 9-cup food processor KFP740.

Title: KitchenAid® Egg Whip
Description: This attachment allows the food processor to be used as a whip for cream and egg whites.

Title: KitchenAid® Feed Tube Pusher
Description: This feed tube pusher helps food through the feed tube when slicing or shredding.

Title: KitchenAid® Work Bowl
Description: This accessory can replace an older KFP740 work bowl or be an extra one to save time by giving you an extra bowl to continue slicing, shredding, chopping, and mixing without stopping to wash and dry your bowl in between batches.

Title: KitchenAid® Citrus Press
Description: This citrus press extracts juice from citrus fruits quickly and thoroughly. Works with both the 9 & 12-cup food processors.

Title: KitchenAid® Disc Set
Description: Every chef needs a multipurpose disc set that allows them to be truly creative in the kitchen. Works with both 9 & 12-cup food processors. This set includes: 6 mm shredding disc, 6 mm slicing disc, French fry cutting disc, Julienne disc, Parmesan/Ice grating disc.

Title: KitchenAid® Julienne Disc
